I"<h2 id="ingredients">Ingredients</h2>

<ul>
  <li>1 stick butter</li>
  <li>1 cup light brown sugar</li>
  <li>1/2 cup granulated sugar</li>
  <li>1 teaspoon vanilla</li>
  <li>1/4 cup water and 2 eggs well beaten</li>
  <li>1 teaspoon salt</li>
  <li>1 cup flour, sifted</li>
  <li>1/2 teaspoon baking soda</li>
  <li>About 1 cup oatmeal</li>
  <li>Chopped nuts (walnuts preferred)</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="directions">Directions</h2>

<p>Mix in order and drop on baking sheet. Bake 400° 7 to 8 minutes. Then
run under broiler to brown</p>
